    with your email address, we may use it to communicate with you regarding our services or any important account information. You can
    choose to opt-out of receiving these notifications whenever you choose to.
</p>

<h3 style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">Data Security</h3>
<p style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
    The security of your information is vital to us, and we take effective and appropriate measures to protect the privacy of your information
    to prevent any unauthorized access or interaction with your data. Nevertheless, we cannot garauntee definite scurity as any method of
    transfer over the Internet is not always secure.
</p>

<h3 style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">Children's Privacy</h3>
<p style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
    Our website and services are not directed to individuals under the age of 13 as we do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
    If you think that we have collected information from a child under 13 without knowledge or intern, please do not hesitate to contact
    us immdeitaley.
</p>


<h3 style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">Changes to this Privacy Policy</h3>
<p style="margin-bottom: 100px; font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
